author: @r125l6
text: Dear Corey,  I've been following your YouTube channel for quite some time now, and I must say, your teaching style is exceptional. From mastering Python basics to diving into advanced concepts, Pandas, Matplotlib, Git, and especially Django, your tutorials have been pivotal in my learning journey as a computer science graduate.  Your ability to explain complex topics with clarity is truly remarkable. Now, as I aspire to become a professional Django developer, I believe there's no one better suited to guide us through Django Rest Framework. Your expertise and knack for breaking down concepts would make a tutorial on Django Rest Framework‚Äîfrom basics to production-ready practices‚Äîa highly valuable resource for aspiring professionals like myself.  Thank you for all the knowledge and inspiration you've shared so far, and I eagerly anticipate any future tutorials you may create.  Best regards, Rasel Rana Bangladesh
